<blockquote>
  <blockquote>
    <blockquote>
      <p dir="ltr">
      <font face="Calibri" style="font-size: 11pt">-A Grab and Go Lunch will be served daily Monday through Friday!<br><br>
      -This will begin Monday, March 23rd!</font></p>
      <p dir="ltr">
      <font face="Calibri" style="font-size: 11pt">-11:00 am to 12:30 pm<br><br>
      -We will be serving from the circle drive east of the elementary school<br><br>
      -A FREE lunch is available for all that are ages 18 years and below*</font></p>
      <p dir="ltr">
      <font face="Calibri" style="font-size: 11pt">-The student MUST be present 
      (state mandated requirement)*<br><br>
      -Please do NOT drop off students<br><br>
      -Dine-in is NOT available<br><br>
      -Please take advantage of this FREE service so we can continue with it 
      until April 6, 2020</font></p>
      <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Calibri">
      <span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: underline">
      *Clarification from State Leadership this morning at 11:00am  3-20-2020</span></font></p>
      <ul>
<li>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 11pt">
        Children need to be present to pick up meals.  They can be in a vehicle 
        or on foot.</span></font></p>
</li>
        <li>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 11pt">
        All meals are FREE (Provided to 18 years and younger)</span></font></p>
</li>
        <li>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Calibri"><span style="font-size: 11pt">
         Exceptions: </span></font>
        </p>
<ul>
<li>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Calibri">
          <span style="font-size: 11pt">(1) 19 year old currently enrolled</span></font></p>
</li>
          <li>
          <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Calibri">
          <span style="font-size: 11pt">(2) Currently enrolled special education 
          students up to 21 years of age</span></font></p>
</li>
        </ul>
</li>
        <li>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Calibri">
        <span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700">Students can be from any 
        district.</span></font></p>
</li>
      </ul>
